messages.message: @Victor Zeng the Cypress tests runs on UAT and aihub-sandbox (and I'm assuming PRs too) have been failing since this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/65898) with the error `Could not find credentials entry with ID 'METRONOME_SANDBOX_API_KEY'`. Do we need to set `METRONOME_API_KEY` in those environments?
